name: WKExtendedRuntimeSessionState
desc: The activation states for an extended runtime session.

items.name: case notStarted
items.desc: The app has not yet started or scheduled the session.

items.name: case scheduled
items.desc: The app has scheduled the session to run at a future date.

items.name: case invalid
items.desc: Either the session has encountered an error, or it has stopped running.
